    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Pico Drift, a racing game that puts your driving skills and reflexes to the test. Customize your car, master the art of drifting, and leave the competition in the dust.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315320/extras/055d6c308eb2e5d821734b1da8fcc408.poster.avif?t=1771499897\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315320/extras/055d6c308eb2e5d821734b1da8fcc408.webm?t=1771499897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315320/extras/055d6c308eb2e5d821734b1da8fcc408.mp4?t=1771499897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the race, dive into the in-game map editor to create your own drift playgrounds and unique challenges. Build a racetrack with carefully planned obstacles, or craft your own city district where you can race through traffic to outrun the cops. We plan to continuously expand the game with more building blocks and new themes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315320/extras/2ba779b807b7ea487cecffd3bcc0a8e5.avif?t=1771499897\" width=1560 height=439 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the iconic racing games of the 2000s and the creativity of modern sandbox titles, Pico Drift aims to deliver a competitive experience for speed enthusiasts!</p>",
